WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
Aku ingin seperti bintang.

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
Kamu seperti bulan.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.670
Selama dunia ada,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.780
